# Global ignores for all Hermes profile packages in this repo.
# Each profile also carries its own .gitignore for local exclusions.

**/.env
**/*.log
**/logs/**
**/home/**
**/sessions/**
**/workspace/**
**/gateway/**
**/plugins/**
**/pairing/**
**/hooks/**
**/skins/**
**/plans/**
**/cache/**
**/images/**
**/audio_cache/**
**/image_cache/**
**/*.db*
**/*.bak.*
**/*.lock
**/*.pid
**/*.json.lock
**/.hermes_history
**/auth.lock
